The paper deals with the regularization of deep neural networks using dropout, which is a popular technique in the field of machine learning. The paper also introduces a new method called expectation-linear dropout neural networks, which is a modification of the standard dropout technique. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
